title: Brent Morin: A Joke about Kids Today
description: Brent Morin jokes about kids today in his Netflix special, "I'm Brent Morin". Grab your tickets at NetflixIsAJokeFest.com to see Brent and your other favorite comedians in the Netflix is a Joke Fest happening April 28th-May 8th in Los Angeles.
